## Task 6: Servlet 层 — 注册路由和 handler

**File to modify:** `src/main/java/com/yottastudios/jira/servlet/JiraBotServlet.java`

### Step 1: Register two new routes in initRoutes()

Find the line:
```java
        postRoutes.put("/template-group/list", jsonEndpoint(this::listTemplateGroups));
```
Add AFTER it:
```java
        postRoutes.put("/template-group/sort", jsonEndpoint(this::sortTemplateGroups));
```

Find the line:
```java
        postRoutes.put("/template/listByGroupId", jsonEndpoint(this::listTemplatesByGroupId));
```
Add AFTER it:
```java
        postRoutes.put("/template/sort", jsonEndpoint(this::sortTemplates));
```

### Step 2: Add sortTemplateGroups handler method

Find the `listTemplateGroups` method (which ends around line 295 with `return groups;` and closing brace). Add the new method AFTER `listTemplateGroups`:

```java
    private Map<String, Object> sortTemplateGroups(HttpServletRequest request) throws Exception {
        UserProfile user = userManager.getRemoteUser(request);
        if (user == null) throw new RuntimeException("未登录");

        TemplateGroupSortRo ro = readJsonBody(request, TemplateGroupSortRo.class);
        if (ro == null || ro.getIds() == null || ro.getIds().isEmpty()) {
            throw new RuntimeException("ids不能为空");
        }
        if (ro.getIds().size() > 200) {
            throw new RuntimeException("ids数量不能超过200");
        }

        templateGroupMapper.batchUpdateSortOrder(ro.getIds());

        Map<String, Object> result = new HashMap<>();
        result.put("success", true);
        return result;
    }
```

### Step 3: Add sortTemplates handler method

Find the `listTemplatesByGroupId` method (which ends around line 1494 with `return items;` and closing brace). Add the new method AFTER `listTemplatesByGroupId`:

```java
    private Map<String, Object> sortTemplates(HttpServletRequest request) throws Exception {
        UserProfile user = userManager.getRemoteUser(request);
        if (user == null) throw new RuntimeException("未登录");

        TemplateSortRo ro = readJsonBody(request, TemplateSortRo.class);
        if (ro == null || ro.getIds() == null || ro.getIds().isEmpty()) {
            throw new RuntimeException("ids不能为空");
        }
        if (ro.getGroupId() <= 0) {
            throw new RuntimeException("groupId非法");
        }
        if (ro.getIds().size() > 200) {
            throw new RuntimeException("ids数量不能超过200");
        }
        // 校验 groupId 是否存在
        TemplateGroup group = templateGroupMapper.getById(ro.getGroupId());
        if (group == null) throw new RuntimeException("group不存在");

        templateMapper.batchUpdateSortOrder(ro.getGroupId(), ro.getIds());

        Map<String, Object> result = new HashMap<>();
        result.put("success", true);
        return result;
    }
```

### Important notes:
- The file already has `import com.yottastudios.jira.ro.*;` (wildcard import), so TemplateGroupSortRo and TemplateSortRo are already accessible.
- The file already has `import java.util.*` and `import java.util.HashMap` etc., so HashMap and Map are available.
- The `readJsonBody` method is statically imported via `import static com.yottastudios.jira.core.support.HttpJsonSupport.*;`
- Follow the exact same pattern as existing handlers (check user login, read RO, validate, call mapper, return result).

## Context

This is a Jira plugin at D:/project/pt-gitlab/jira/jirabot/. The servlet file is large (~1600 lines). Be careful with edits - read the file first to understand the structure, then make precise edits. Do NOT rewrite the entire file.

## Your Job

1. Read the servlet file first
2. Make the 3 precise edits (2 route registrations + 2 handler methods)
3. Do NOT commit
4. Report back with status and what was changed

